                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Hero Xtreme 125R:</span> Is more fuel-efficient, with a mileage of around <span class="font-weight-700">66 kmpl</span>, making it a more economical option for daily riders focused on long-term savings.</li>
                </ul>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">BikeCarHub Verdict:</span> For those looking for better fuel efficiency, Hero Xtreme 125R is the clear winner.</p>

