                    <li>Single-channel ABS for better safety</li>
                    <li>Engine cut-off on side stand</li>
                </ul>

                <p><span class="font-weight-700">BikeCarHub Verdict:</span> When it comes to technology, the Ntorq 125 is clearly ahead with its smart connectivity features, while the Xtreme 125R focuses on basic but reliable safety features.</p>

