                <p><span class="font-weight-700">BikeCarHub Verdict:</span> If smart features and comfort are a priority, the Ntorq 125 offers good value. For those who want better mileage, sporty motorcycle styling, and highway readiness, the Xtreme 125R offers excellent value.</p>
