                <p>The <span class="font-weight-700">TVS Ntorq 125</span> is the right choice for riders who want a smart, stylish, and convenient scooter with tech features that make commuting enjoyable.</p>
                <p>The <span class="font-weight-700">Hero Xtreme 125R</span> is better suited for those who prefer motorcycles, want a sporty look, high fuel efficiency, and the ability to occasionally ride on highways.</p>
                <p>Ultimately, both are solid options in the 125cc segment. Buyers should choose based on their riding style, distance, and whether they prefer a scooter or a motorcycle.</p>

